Global Luggage Bag Sales Market Insights
Luggage Bag Sales Market size was valued at USD 23.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 32.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Luggage Bag Sales Market Overview
The global luggage bag sales market has experienced significant growth over the last few years. The increasing number of international travelers, along with rising disposable incomes, has propelled the demand for luggage products. The market was valued at approximately USD 24.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.2% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is largely driven by the development of innovative, lightweight, and durable luggage options, alongside rising tourism. The market is also seeing an increasing preference for premium, high-quality luggage options due to the growing trend of luxury travel. These factors collectively indicate a bright outlook for the luggage bag sales industry in the coming years.

